description: BKeD is truckin’ through the streets of Charleston and serving up a choice selection of sandwiches and sweet treats. A few of the beautifully tasty items you’ll find on their rotational menu include...The Eggplant Melt-with roasted peppers, goat cheese, mozzarella, and pesto herbed mayoTurkey Club- with crispy bacon, fresh greens, pickled red onions, and gouda cheeseCurry Chicken Salad Sandwich- with cranberry chutney and fresh greens...as well as fresh-baked artisan pretzels, fantastically flavorful fig pop tarts, and creamy banana pudding… just to name a few. For all this and much more, come take a brisk trip out to BKed!
name: BKeD
